Package: nuba-lang
Version: 1.0.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8)
Maintainer: Nuba Language Project <hello@nuba-lang.org>
Homepage: https://nuba-lang.org
Description: Nuba Programming Language
 Nuba is a clean, expressive, dynamically-typed programming language
 that runs .nu files just like Python runs .py files.
 .
 Features:
  - Variables (let/const), all data types
  - Functions, lambdas, closures
  - Classes with single inheritance
  - Pattern matching (match/case)
  - Error handling (try/catch/finally)
  - 70+ built-in functions
  - Standard library
  - Interactive REPL
 .
 After installation, run .nu files with:
   nuba myfile.nu
 .
 Or start the interactive REPL:
   nuba
